IntIter

type
class
available in
neko, flash9, php, flash8, flash7, flash6
Integer iterator. Used for interval implementation.

Constructor

public new(min : Int, max : Int)
Iterate from min (inclusive) to max (exclusive). If max <= min, the iterator will not act as a countdown.

Instance Variables

private max : Int

private min : Int

Instance Methods

public hasNext() : Bool

public next() : Int
